statements: SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE participant_id = 1;
SELECT scan_result, scan_timestamp FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE eye_movement_pattern = 'Stable';
SELECT participant_id, eye_movement_pattern FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE scan_result = 'Normal' ORDER BY scan_timestamp DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT participant_id FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE eye_movement_pattern = 'Erratic';
SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningData ORDER BY scan_timestamp ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE participant_id = 1;
SELECT participant_id, scan_timestamp FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE scan_result = 'Positive' ORDER BY scan_timestamp DESC;
SELECT participant_id, COUNT(*) AS total_scans FROM RetinaScanningData GROUP BY participant_id HAVING total_scans > 2;
SELECT DISTINCT participant_id, eye_movement_pattern FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE scan_timestamp >= '2022-01-01' AND scan_timestamp < '2022-02-01';
SELECT AVG(CAST(participant_id AS FLOAT)) AS avg_id, MAX(scan_timestamp) AS latest_scan FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE scan_result = 'Negative';
SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningData ORDER BY scan_time DESC;
SELECT participant_id, x_coordinate, y_coordinate FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE participant_id = 101;
SELECT * FROM EyeMovementPatterns WHERE average_movement_speed > 5.0;
SELECT pattern_id, pattern_description FROM EyeMovementPatterns WHERE pattern_confidence >= 0.8 ORDER BY pattern_id ASC;
SELECT participant_id, COUNT(*) AS scan_count FROM RetinaScanningData GROUP BY participant_id;
SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE participant_id = 1 ORDER BY scan_time DESC;
SELECT participant_id, x_coordinate, y_coordinate FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE y_coordinate > 50;
SELECT pattern_id, pattern_description FROM EyeMovementPatterns WHERE average_movement_speed < 2.0 AND pattern_confidence > 0.8;
SELECT participant_id, COUNT(*) AS total_scans FROM RetinaScanningData GROUP BY participant_id;
SELECT * FROM EyeMovementPatterns WHERE pattern_id IN (1, 3, 5) ORDER BY pattern_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningData;
SELECT participant_id, timestamp, x_coordinate, y_coordinate FROM RetinaScanningData ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM ResearchStudies WHERE start_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT study_id, study_name, researcher_id FROM ResearchStudies WHERE end_date <= '2022-12-31';
SELECT pattern_id, participant_id, pattern_type FROM EyeMovementPatterns WHERE pattern_count > 10 ORDER BY pattern_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE participant_id = 10 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT study_name, researcher_id, end_date FROM ResearchStudies WHERE start_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT participant_id, pattern_type FROM EyeMovementPatterns WHERE pattern_count > 100 ORDER BY participant_id ASC, pattern_count DESC;
SELECT participant_id, COUNT(pattern_id) AS pattern_count FROM EyeMovementPatterns GROUP BY participant_id ORDER BY pattern_count DESC;
SELECT RS.study_name, EP.pattern_type FROM ResearchStudies RS JOIN EyeMovementPatterns EP ON RS.researcher_id = EP.participant_id WHERE RS.end_date > '2022-06-30';
SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningData;
SELECT participant_id, scan_time FROM RetinaScanningData ORDER BY scan_time DESC;
SELECT participant_id, COUNT(*) AS num_scans FROM RetinaScanningData GROUP BY participant_id;
SELECT r.*, p.participant_name FROM ResearchStudies r JOIN StudyParticipants p ON r.study_id = p.participant_id;
SELECT * FROM EyeMovementPatterns WHERE pattern_description LIKE '%interesting%' ORDER BY pattern_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningData;
SELECT participant_id, scan_time FROM RetinaScanningData ORDER BY scan_time DESC;
SELECT * FROM StudyParticipants WHERE participant_age > 30;
SELECT participant_name, participant_gender FROM StudyParticipants WHERE participant_gender = 'Female';
SELECT pattern_name, pattern_description FROM EyeMovementPatterns WHERE pattern_id <= 3;
SELECT * FROM Retina_Scanning_Participants;
SELECT participant_name, age FROM Retina_Scanning_Participants WHERE age > 30;
SELECT session_date, duration_minutes FROM Retina_Scanning_Sessions ORDER BY session_date DESC;
SELECT pattern_description FROM Eye_Movement_Patterns WHERE pattern_id = 3;
SELECT study_name, start_date, end_date FROM Research_Studies WHERE end_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM Retina_Scanning_Participants ORDER BY participant_id DESC;
SELECT participant_name, age FROM Retina_Scanning_Participants WHERE gender = 'Male';
SELECT * FROM Retina_Scanning_Sessions WHERE duration_minutes > 30 ORDER BY session_date ASC;
SELECT pattern_description, pattern_id FROM Eye_Movement_Patterns JOIN Retina_Scanning_Data ON Eye_Movement_Patterns.data_id = Retina_Scanning_Data.data_id;
SELECT study_id, study_name, start_date, end_date FROM Research_Studies WHERE start_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
